{"post_payload": {"contentType": "article", "type": "article", "contentIdentity": "work", "title": "西湖亲子半日城市漫游路线", "summary": "把湖边步行、咖啡歇脚和回酒店的回撤节奏放进同一篇游记里，更适合冷启动内容生产。", "coverUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_article_001/v1/cover.png", "tags": ["theme_city_walk", "scene_weekend_daytrip", "audience_family", "quality_high_confidence"], "locationName": "杭州西湖", "visibility": "public", "assistantUsePolicy": "inherit", "authorId": "fixture_user_travel", "authorDisplayNameSnapshot": "契约旅行家", "authorAvatarUrlSnapshot": "media/avatar/user/fixture_user_travel/v1/avatar.png", "sourceType": "cold_start_batch", "sourcePostId": "west_lake_article_001_article_001", "articleDocument": {"template": "journal", "fontPreset": "clean", "coverImageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_article_001/v1/cover.png", "titleStyle": "major", "nodes": [{"id": "title", "type": "documentTitle", "text": "西湖亲子半日城市漫游路线"}, {"id": "paragraph_1", "type": "paragraph", "text": "如果是带孩子在西湖玩半天，建议把步行主段压缩在白堤和断桥附近。"}, {"id": "paragraph_2", "type": "paragraph", "text": "下午中段安排龙井路咖啡补给，既能休息，也能给内容里补上本地生活节点。"}, {"id": "paragraph_3", "type": "paragraph", "text": "傍晚前回到西湖亲子友好酒店，方便整理照片和第二天继续延展路线。"}, {"id": "figure_1", "type": "figure", "imageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_article_001/v1/cover.png", "imageLayout": "fullWidth", "caption": "西湖傍晚封面"}, {"id": "figure_2", "type": "figure", "imageUrl": "media/image/post/west_lake_article_001/v1/hotel.png", "imageLayout": "fullWidth", "caption": "亲子酒店外立面"}]}}, "semantic": {"entity_refs": ["trees/entities/地点/西湖.yaml", "trees/entities/住宿/西湖亲子友好酒店.yaml", "trees/entities/本地生活/龙井路咖啡.yaml"], "tag_refs": ["trees/tags/主题/城市漫游.yaml", "trees/tags/场景/周末一日.yaml", "trees/tags/人群/亲子.yaml", "trees/tags/质量/高置信.yaml"], "source_urls": ["https://www.mafengwo.cn/i/west-lake-family-halfday"]}}
